#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

unsigned encore_to(unsigned n)
{
	unsigned p=n;
	while(p)
	{
		n=n+p%10;
		p/=10;
	}
	return n;
}

int main()
{
	int t;
	unsigned n,i;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		cin>>n;
		for(i=20;i<n;i++)
		if(encore_to(i)==n) break;
		if(i==n) cout<<"NONE\n";
		else cout<<i<<endl;	
	}
	return 0;
}
